Why should she be?

25
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,411
One moment.

26
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,451
Excuse me.

27
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,529
She doesn't know me at all.

28
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,364
Oh please!
She was six.

29
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,321
She doesn't even have my address.

30
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,962
It's not my business any more.

31
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:42,650
You wanted Martha for yourself,
so cope with this on your own.

32
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,845
Who was that?

33
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:59,330
Sylvia.

34
