57
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,211
Hello?

58
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,928
Oh, it's you.
- I forgot my key.

59
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,761
Were you expecting someone else?

60
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,761
I did some shopping.
Shall I cook?

61
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,005
Great.

62
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:21,005
Here.

63
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:24,125
One like this.

64
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,771
And a pair of jeans.

65
